Speaker 1: No problem. Uh, can I get your name and zip code?

Speaker 1: 2167 Crane Highway?

Speaker 2: Yes, sir.

Speaker 1: Okay. You want to do the 25 pills again?

Speaker 2: Yes, sir.

Speaker 1: Okay. No problem.

Speaker 2: And then am I good to use the Visa and then 5255?

Speaker 1: Yes, sir.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: Alright, Joseph. We're all set. I hope you enjoy your weekend.

Speaker 2: This will be, uh, sent to the pharmacy to ship out.

Speaker 1: Okay. Thank you.

Speaker 2: Thanks. Bye-bye.
